{
  "id": "RAW_03d91b11",
  "title": "多位大佬点赞，不用 PS、不写 Prompt，这个 AI 直接生成设计源文件",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIwMTU5OTQ1Nw==&mid=2653725487&idx=1&sn=9801c074455464ebe85ff59dae1b6eee",
  "date": "2026-03-10 08:15:00",
  "author": " (沃垠AI)",
  "siteName": "沃垠AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大家好，我是冷逸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">早上刷x，发现一个从来没听过的 AI 设计工具，被145k粉丝的网红博主 Ding 转发了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmka8j8moai\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241838\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b6ddd630&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FH9yPeQXaIQjgcm4GMNianZDsLQeSv07SXAUW5Uciad4wYxzWuBuN8tkbsxDzXicosgnM1Usw2ebyrsZ3gG8Wm9Z8JJe0WmLBrTB3QibrBR2XzyM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">好奇心瞬间被勾起：到底什么项目能让这些大佬也觉得新鲜？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">结果一查，发现是国内 Seede AI 团队在海外发布的新品:&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Veeso AI</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">体验了半小时后，我意识到一件事。这玩意跟市面上那些「文生图」AI 设计工具，完全不是一个物种。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmivw2uuw70\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241779\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3df9114e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FH9yPeQXaIQjjA887BvMP9T7axRpPfwicxDfL1ZebOmx4g3LAyn4jumXOuEXnuFQiaxgqstcvjcPQltyJz4vamn7VVVGPduGyf8LmmVUic61A4c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Seede 不是做修图，不是 PS，它完全走了 AI 设计的另一个新方向，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">生成的不仅是可以直接用的图片素材，还是可以继续编辑、复用、反复修改的设计源文件。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">还能导出 PSD，把最后一公里都做了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">更离谱的是，它连提示词都不用写。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">现在有很多 AI 生图产品，第一次玩的时候觉得很惊艳，但真有设计需求的时候，你会发现要研究画风、了解排版逻辑，还要把这些整理成 AI 能听懂的“咒语”，用 AI 设计的门槛一点也不比 PS 低。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI 终于不再是终点，而是设计流程的起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506236477\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2b71a2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvic8DcjbZP6CtUD7nHjdLA0fB0eibP1sbkJBqTVafECcdFc416I0ia2VHw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">一手体验</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">大家先跟随我的视角，沉浸式体验一下，Seede AI 是如何将 AI 设计带入源文件时代的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">进入网址</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;\">seede.ai</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，告诉 Seede AI，你想创作什么内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Seede AI 提供了长图、海报、PPT、宣传册等常见的设计场景供选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmivw6yr1bec\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241780\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7a06f475&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FH9yPeQXaIQhKHzibGrJV6hflWI1zejvAHl6uCFFKdO5J06zXRbhdicaz03fY4icF6kavPuntYvU96tDlT1h4W6GEl9bIYwCQTNqVjSicZfh1gQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和 AI 生图工具最大的区别是，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">我们甚至都不需要写提示词</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，比如描述画面、排版、风格这些，统统不用管。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">我们只用告诉 Seede AI，设计中需要展现哪些文字信息，就可以了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">还可以上传参考设计稿和生成设计所需的素材</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。Seede AI 会自动完成设计稿创作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">1）一键制作易拉宝</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">比如，最近小龙虾很火爆，我想做一个实战训练营的易拉宝宣传图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">选择易拉宝，Seede AI 会自动调整好图片尺寸要求（当然，也支持自定义尺寸）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">输入相关的文案信息：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:left;background-position-y:top;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">活动主题：OpenClaw 实战训练营</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">时间：2026年4月1日-2026年4月3日</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【训练营简介】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">3天高强度实战，围绕 OpenClaw 的核心能力展开系统训练，带你了解本地部署、技能调用、任务执行、记忆机制与实际工作流搭建。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">课程会结合真实使用场景，帮助学员从了解概念走到亲手跑通，让 OpenClaw 真正进入日常办公、内容创作与自动化协作流程中。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【导师阵容】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">冷逸（沃垠 AI 创始人）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">Peter Steinberger（OpenClaw 创始人）</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【训练营亮点】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">从基础认知到实操搭建，完整覆盖 OpenClaw 的核心使用路径。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">课程内容聚焦真实问题，包含安装配置、常见报错排查、技能接入、审批机制、记忆管理与多场景任务演示。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">学完之后，能够独立完成一套可用的 OpenClaw 工作流，真正把它变成能帮你干活的 AI 助手。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【适合人群】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;适合希望提升效率的内容创作者、产品经理、独立开发者，以及想亲自体验 Agent 工作流的普通用户。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">即使没有太强的技术背景，也可以通过案例拆解和现场演练，快速理解 OpenClaw 的使用逻辑与核心价值。</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【课程安排】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Day 1：认识 OpenClaw 与基础环境搭建</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上午：OpenClaw 能做什么，适合哪些任务场景</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;下午：本地部署、目录配置、基础命令与常见问题排查</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">Day 2：技能、记忆与任务执行实战</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上午：Skills 使用方法、审批机制、任务拆解逻辑</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;下午：文件整理、信息收集、内容生成等案例演练</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">Day 3：工作流搭建与进阶应用</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;上午：结合个人需求设计专属 OpenClaw 工作流</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;下午：实战演示、成果展示与使用经验分享</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">【训练营收获】</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;掌握 OpenClaw 的基础部署与使用方法</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;理解 Skills、记忆与审批机制的作用</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;学会搭建适合自己工作场景的自动化流程</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;完成一个可直接落地的 OpenClaw 实战案例</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">继续上传设计稿需要用到的图片素材：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmiwbticp0c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5581395348837209\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1376\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241826\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7d2e1008&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FH9yPeQXaIQiavibzoKbODhoJnsa8nlvnKR3aTx5sFKarMsWz76lclRAGyPPjCWvp1e9pTwibPQ0G3dAxrE81UkQ5nL9okYEwnpUpBET559Yz7c%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">别较真，这图片是AI生成的<img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"20\" style=\"display:inline-block;width:20px;vertical-align:middle;background-size:cover;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7478ac68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fres.wx.qq.com%2Ft%2Fwx_fed%2Fwe-emoji%2Fres%2Fassets%2Fnewemoji%2FYellowdog.png\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们可以直接指定图片的用途，比如这张大合照，用作产品图片素材，上传图片后点击图片就可以设置：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmiwevjo1kv5\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241783\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cce5619f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FH9yPeQXaIQjaSyJ3CZ0q7vVDzj0t5EfjBic9tjauhOibxZMe88I2PkSqMGo3CmhpduFszXhM00ACC2L9kUIWAfxTT6SciaLkL6kUia3cwMwpaUU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图片对应部分的文字描述，我们可以直接将图片拖拽放在旁边，并添加描述，Seede AI 会自动处理好图文对应关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在导师介绍这里添加头像，只需要把图片拖动在导师介绍旁边，添加图片用途——人物，或者人物照片。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmiwf028d4e\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5625579240037072\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241784\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=abce1b8e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FH9yPeQXaIQh9kfBauOweMrniaXUmkxujGb6NIHTaiczwrCc8efDlG6d1xvyQerLuH2XEF85mEYD65aDWRTuoBkhCMnjuGuyItjfDXRWqian4OU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在输入框选择主题色，Seede AI 提供了一些经典配色主题，供我们选择。同时也可以选择智能适配，让 AI 根据内容自由发挥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Seede AI 接入了海内外前端设计的顶流模型，比如 Kimi K2.5，Gemini 3.1 Pro，Claude 4.6等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmiwlt1l1apb\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7415413533834586\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1064\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241785\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0600e5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FH9yPeQXaIQjr2HWnwXBc8LU1SfodspuuhWQiasdzEZDnY4zVShqibkSiaUYgPHmjDketGe3QUs4yFhOtaXmb4ZHUlaeicnibfa4tPGRZ10ianSyjE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不到一分钟，就生成好了设计稿。我们一起看看最终生成的结果：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mmiwm2d71nka\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"5.226851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2160\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"506241827\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86bb4a9d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FH9yPeQXaIQiaqQiaYz5ZnJgvu0Puy3mgmekibca8FcAOOFvVzADEVGaTQWVgPCB5mw7gTSPBAN9ic537Msncv3QKRFOxk4W4kG8eX4V6aGY3BdM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文案部分和我们提供的文本完全一致，图片的位置和用途也和我们的要求完全匹配。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span l